msgctxt "1672"
msgid "Number One Hostess"
msgstr "Hostess numero uno"

msgctxt "1676"
msgid "Number Two Hostess"
msgstr "Hostess numero dos"

msgctxt "1680"
msgid "Talk_No"
msgstr "Talk_No"

msgctxt "1684"
msgid "Talk_NoBig"
msgstr "Talk_NoBig"

msgctxt "84_Number One Hostess"
msgid "Don't I look great with this bag? Well? What do you think?"
msgstr "¿No me veo bien con esta bolsa? ¿Bueno? ¿Qué piensas?"

msgctxt "96_Number Two Hostess"
msgid "I dunno... Maybe it's a little too flashy for you, Aki-san? It's more of my style, to be honest."
msgstr "No sé... ¿Quizás es demasiado llamativo para ti, Aki-san? Es más de mi estilo, para ser honesto."

msgctxt "108_Number One Hostess"
msgid "Really? But it's so expensive. Don't you think it's a little soon for you to have something like this?"
msgstr "¿Enserio? Pero eso es muy caro. ¿No crees que es demasiado pronto para pedir algo como eso?"

msgctxt "120_Number Two Hostess"
msgid "Huh? Wait, are you planning on buying this with your own money!? Why don't you get like, a guy to buy it for you or something!?"
msgstr "¿Eh? Espera, ¿¡estás planeando comprar esto con tu propio dinero!? ¿¡Por qué no te consigues a un tipo para que te lo compre o algo así!?"

msgctxt "132_Number One Hostess"
msgid "If there's something I really like, I buy it myself. I don't like to abuse my customers like that. They're not our own little piggybanks, you know?"
msgstr "Si hay algo que realmente me gusta, lo compro yo misma. No me gusta abusar de mis clientes así. No son nuestros alcancias personales, ¿sabes?"

msgctxt "144_Number Two Hostess"
msgid "I know! It's just, I think I look so much better than you with this bag..."
msgstr "¡Lo sé! Es solo que creo que me veo mucho mejor que tú con este bolso..."

